\u3002\n\n\u79fb\u52a8\u65b9\u5f0f\u501f\u9274\u4e86Gorilla Tag\uff0c\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u4ec5\u4ec5\u53ea\u7528\u53cc\u624b\u6765\u8dd1\u3001\u8df3\u548c\u51fb\u7403\u3002\u6e38\u620f\u89c4\u5219\u548c\u7f8e\u5f0f\u6a44\u6984\u7403\u76f8\u540c\u3002\n\n\u9664\u4e86\u6a44\u6984\u7403\u4e4b\u5916\uff0c\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u8fd8\u6709\u8db3\u7403\u3001\u68d2\u7403\u3001\u8eb2\u907f\u7403\u7b49\u8bb8\u591a\u6bd4\u8d5b\u6a21\u5f0f\u3002\n\n\u6e38\u620f\u662f\u514d\u8d39\u7684\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u53ef\u4ee5\u548c\u5176\u4ed6\u4eba\u540c\u573a\u7ade\u6280\u3002", "short_description": "\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u626e\u6f14\u4e00\u53ea\u7329\u7329\u6765\u73a9\u7f8e\u5f0f\u6a44\u6984\u7403\uff01"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "510966481973542", "locale": "en_GB", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Gorilla Football", "keywords": ["football", "sports", "basketball"], "long_description": "This is an interesting VR sports competitive game. You play as a gorilla.\n\nThe locomotion is inspired by Gorilla Tag. You can run, jump, and control the ball using only your hands. The rules are similar to American football.\n\nBesides football, there are also many other modes, such as soccer, baseball and dodgeball.\n\nThis game is free, and you can play with other players.", "short_description": "You can play American football as a gorilla with other players!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://web.manyatang.com/gorilla_football/privacy_policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Fengu Studio", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://web.manyatang.com/gorilla_football", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED"